text: Club Sport Marítimo Sub-23 is a Portuguese football club that currently plays in the Campeonato Nacional de Sub-23. They are the second reserve team of Club Sport Marítimo. They play their home games at the Campo da Imaculada Conceição in the suburb of Santo António in Funchal, Madeira. ==External links== *ZeroZero.pt profile Category:C.S.
